Interface DataCheckConfiguration

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
DataCheckConfigurationImpl
public interface DataCheckConfiguration
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Data Check Configuration'. Network data check configuration

The following features are supported:

  • Turn Off Island Bus
  • Auto Turn Line2 Xfr

isAutoTurnLine2Xfr

boolean isAutoTurnLine2Xfr()
Returns the value of the 'Auto Turn Line2 Xfr' attribute. The default value is "false". When line branch is with different base voltage at from/to side, turn the line branch to a xfr branch.

Returns:
the value of the 'Auto Turn Line2 Xfr' attribute.
